001package edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.service;
002
003import edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dto.Authentication;
004import edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dto.MeetingDetailsResponse;
005import edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dto.MeetingListResponse;
006import edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dto.MeetingParticipantsResponse;
007import edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dto.UserListResponse;
008import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Single;
009import retrofit2.http.Field;
010import retrofit2.http.FormUrlEncoded;
011import retrofit2.http.GET;
012import retrofit2.http.Header;
013import retrofit2.http.Headers;
014import retrofit2.http.POST;
015import retrofit2.http.Path;
016import retrofit2.http.Query;
017
018public interface ZoomApiProxy {
019
020
021  @GET("users/{userId}/meetings")
022  Single<MeetingListResponse> listMeetings(@Header("Authorization") String bearerToken, @Path("userId") String userId, @Query("next_page_token") String nextPageToken, @Query("from") String from, @Query("to") String to, @Query("page_size") int pageSize, @Query("type") String meetingType);
023
024  @GET("past_meetings/{meetingId}/participants")
025  Single<MeetingParticipantsResponse> listParticipants(@Header("Authorization") String bearerToken, @Path("meetingId")String meetingId, @Query("next_page_token") String nextPageToken);
026
027  @GET("users")
028  Single<UserListResponse> listUsers(@Header("Authorization") String bearerToken,  @Query("next_page_token") String nextPageToken, @Query("page_size") int pageSize);
029
030  @GET("meetings/{meetingId}")
031  Single<MeetingDetailsResponse> getDetails(@Header("Authorization") String bearerToken, @Path("meetingId") long meetingId);
032
033}
